Class Showtime

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Showtime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Showtime
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class contains all information of a showtime - including its Movie, Cinema, Date and a 2D array of Seat.
